node.text: That’s the lovely #Gardensbythebay in #Singapore.  While The country still is following the #circuitbreakersg, I just head out everyday for my walk.  Yesterday, I witnessed this amazing Super trees.  Gardens by the Bay brings to life the National Parks Board Singapore's vision of creating a City in a Garden. Isn’t that amazing ? The Gardens captures the essence of Singapore as the premier tropical Garden City with the perfect environment in which to live and work - making Singapore a leading global city of the 21st century.  #visit_singapore #instagram #Shotoniphone #iphonography #shotoniphone11pro #travel #visualart #visualsoflife #visitsingapore #mobilephotography #photooftheday #photography #yourshotphotographer #yourshot_india #natgeoyourshot
Beautiful picture. Follow my Photography account @decideyourframe and I'll follow you from here. 💕🌸
